 Yeah, and we have systems like this already

04:15.080 --> 04:20.000
 that make many decisions for ourselves in society

04:20.000 --> 04:22.640
 that need to be designed in a way that they...

04:22.640 --> 04:24.200
 Like, you know, rules about things

