 that sometimes have bad side effects.

04:27.520 --> 04:29.600
 And we have to be flexible enough about those rules

04:29.600 --> 04:31.600
 so that they can be broken when it's obvious

04:31.600 --> 04:33.000
 that they shouldn't be applied.

