 I think it should be a bit like in the design

05:47.480 --> 05:51.960
 of autonomous AI systems.

05:51.960 --> 05:54.200
 There should be the equivalent of, you know,

05:54.200 --> 05:59.040
 the oath that hypocrites oaths

